replyContent: Thanks for this feedback. On the Confirm Trip page, you should see a Connection Times option. You can use this to set the minimum transfer time for this trip.

To use this app in Sydney trains: 1 min means Now,  Now means just left.
replyContent: Well yes, to clarify - the data in TripView is accurate to the minute (not to the second). TripView will start displaying "Now" at the scheduled departure time. For example, if the train is scheduled to depart at 7:00, it will show "Now" from 7:00:00 until 7:00:59. At 7:01:00, it will change to show "1 min ago".
